Toyota minivan orders exceed sales target . Toyota Motor Corp said on Wednesday it had received 36 , 000 orders for its new TownAce Noah and LiteAce Noah recreational vehicles in the month after their launch in Japan . Toyota launched the two models on October 23 with a total monthly sales target of 6 , 500 units . Toyota ' s 33 . 4 percent owned Daihatsu Motor Co Ltd makes the TownAce Noah and LiteAce Noah . Daihatsu ' s Ikeda plant in Osaka , western Japan , will operate for six extra days in December to keep up with orders , a Toyota spokesman said . 
